{"tid":588873,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"游蕙禎不談補選：唔通叫人投2號（鄭泳舜）","createTime":"2018-03-11T13:43:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T14:40:17.000Z","uid":53379,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cfae0cd758245ecf165d506900ea63b5f85f9aca","tid":588873,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T13:43:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">游蕙禎不談補選：唔通叫人投2號（鄭泳舜）咩</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180311/s00001/d4403e0cb2b559d425eed7ac717a2a61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180311%2Fs00001%2Fd4403e0cb2b559d425eed7ac717a2a61.jpg&h=c8496095&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這次立法會補選的九龍西和新界東議席，原本分別屬於青年新政游蕙禎和梁頌恆，唯二人在補選前夕無呼籲市民投票，二人的社交網站專頁，亦不見任何有關補選的帖文。游蕙禎回應本報查詢時表示，曾經說過不會公開支持任何一個候選人，以免變成「死亡之吻」，因此「不會自打嘴巴」，談任何有關補選的事。游說：「我出得聲，唔通係叫人投2號（民建聯鄭泳舜）咩」。<br />\n<br />\n梁頌恆早前曾形容是次選舉「經n重篩選」，根本不能表達民意，不明白是次選舉的意義何在。<br />\n<br />\n九龍西其他候選人包括姚松炎和蔡東洲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180311/s00001/1520774577522\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180311%2Fs00001%2F1520774577522&d=F5sMjSI3WuEVncdZncxgMbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=d822ff4c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180311%2Fs00001%2F1520774577522&h=a13a09ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180311/s00001/1520774577522</a>"},{"pid":"65536166fd08e4745b6248ae0c20101941cd51ff","tid":588873,"uid":34005,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T13:44:34.000Z","msg":"係啲on9焦土撚話要投對家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac3f80b42600f221cdbffefc4aef806c2fb2fcd","tid":588873,"uid":91152,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T13:46:16.000Z","msg":"<img 